  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我们需要画一个序列图来展示Redis缓存集群里的ARP解析过程。场景是四台电脑通过交换机通信，我想突出MAC地址学习机制。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Computadora A",
        "Computadora B",
        "Computadora C",
        "Computadora D",
        "Switch"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白。这四台电脑里，A和C属于Redis缓存节点，B和D是Worker节点对吗？还有交换机本身也是Redis缓存基础设施的一部分？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Infra_WorkerNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对的。A和C跑Redis，B和D跑计算任务。交换机作为网络层设备，我打算标注它也属于Redis缓存的基础设施范畴，强调这是缓存集群的内部网络。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Switch",
        "Infra_RedisCache"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "好的，我按从左到右排：A、交换机、B、C、D。这样A到C的跨交换机通信路径比较清晰。初始状态我在交换机上方加个注释，说明MAC表是空的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Switch",
        "Note over S"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "可以。然后进入第一阶段，A要发ARP请求找C的MAC地址。这里有个细节：A的ARP包源地址要标成IngressController，目标广播地址标成EtcdCluster。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A",
        "ARP Request",
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加A到交换机的ARP Request箭头，标注了源是A的IngressController，目标是Broadcast的EtcdCluster。交换机收到后应该在旁边加个注释，记录它从端口1学到了A的MAC。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A-S",
        "Note over S",
        "Puerto 1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "没错，交换机 flooding 这个广播包。接下来画三条从交换机出去的箭头，分别到B、C、D。但注意标注：到B和D的标IngressController，到C的标EtcdCluster，因为C才是Etcd集群的节点。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S-B",
        "S-C",
        "S-D",
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "这里我有点疑惑。ARP请求的目标IP是C的，但广播包本身应该一视同仁。您说的标注差异是指我们在图里用不同基础设施标签来区分它们的角色归属，而不是包内容不同？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "ARP Request",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_IngressController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "正是这个意思。所有ARP请求包内容一样，但我想在图里体现：B和D作为WorkerNode收到的是IngressController发起的查询，而C作为Redis缓存节点同时属于EtcdCluster，它是被查询的目标。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "B",
        "D",
        "C",
        "Infra_WorkerNode",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "理解了，已添加S到B、C、D的三条ARP Request箭头，分别按您说的标注了基础设施归属。接下来是第二阶段ARP响应？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S-B",
        "S-C",
        "S-D"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对。在B和D上方加个注释，说明只有C会响应ARP。然后C发单播响应给交换机，源地址标成LoadBalancer，目标标回A的RedisCache。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Note over B,D",
        "C-S",
        "ARP Response",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
        "Infra_RedisCache"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加注释和C到交换机的ARP Response。交换机这里也要更新注释，记录从端口3学到了C的MAC地址。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "C-S",
        "Note over S",
        "Puerto 3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "端口3对应C的位置对吧？确认一下。然后交换机把响应单播给A，这条箭头标IngressController。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Puerto 3",
        "S-A",
        "Infra_IngressController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，C在交换机右边第三个位置，对应端口3。S到A的ARP Response已添加，标注IngressController。现在进入第三阶段直接通信？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S-A",
        "Infra_IngressController"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 15,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "没错。A现在知道C的MAC了，开始发数据。画A到交换机的数据箭头，标注\"Datos para C\"，源IngressController，目标EtcdCluster。",
      "elements_involved": [],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 16,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加数据发送箭头。交换机这边需要体现查表过程吧？我在交换机上方加注释，说明它查询MAC表，找到C在端口3。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A-S",
        "Note over S",
        "Tabla MAC",
        "Puerto 3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 17,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "等等，这里有个问题。我之前说A到C的数据目标标EtcdCluster，但C本身属于RedisCache，只是它同时跑Etcd。让我想想——",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A",
        "C",
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 18,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "我注意到矛盾了。A发给C的数据，如果目标是EtcdCluster，但C的标注是RedisCache。或者您的意思是：数据层面走EtcdCluster协议，但物理节点还是RedisCache？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Datos",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_RedisCache"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 19,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "不对，是我搞混了。ARP请求阶段用EtcdCluster是因为广播查询目标IP属于Etcd集群，但数据阶段A和C都是RedisCache节点之间的通信。数据箭头的目标应该标RedisCache，不是EtcdCluster。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "A-S",
        "Datos",
        "Infra_RedisCache"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 20,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已修正，A到交换机的数据箭头现在目标标注为RedisCache。交换机查表后转发到C，最后这条S到C的数据箭头目标也保持一致吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S-C",
        "Datos",
        "Infra_RedisCache"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 21,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "最后这条S到C的，目标标EtcdCluster。因为交换机转发时查到的表项是之前ARP阶段关联到EtcdCluster上下文的，这样体现MAC表条目的来源记忆。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S-C",
        "Datos",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 22,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "明白了，体现转发决策基于之前的ARP学习上下文。S到C的数据箭头已添加，目标标注EtcdCluster。整个流程现在完整了：ARP广播学习、单播响应、精准转发。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "S-C",
        "FASE 3",
        "Comunicación Directa"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 23,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "还有个小优化。在A和D上方加个总注释，把三个阶段标清楚：FASE 1 ARP Request，FASE 2 ARP Response，FASE 3 Comunicación Directa。这样读者一眼看清时序。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Note over A,D",
        "FASE 1",
        "FASE 2",
        "FASE 3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 24,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已添加三个阶段的注释，分别放在对应时序位置的上方。检查一下：A的IngressController角色贯穿始终，C的双重身份在ARP请求和数据转发阶段有体现，MAC地址学习路径清晰。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Note over A,D",
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 25,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "完美。这个图现在能清楚展示Redis缓存集群内部，ARP协议如何让交换机从广播学习到精准转发的完整过程。特别是突出了基础设施组件的交叉归属关系。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Infra_RedisCache",
        "Infra_IngressController",
        "Infra_EtcdCluster",
        "Infra_LoadBalancer",
        "Infra_WorkerNode"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    }
  ],
